<html>
<head>

  <title>ICRTET2016</title>
  <meta charset='utf-8' />
  <%= stylesheet_link_tag    'application', media: 'all', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  <%= javascript_include_tag 'application', 'data-turbolinks-track' => true %>
  <%= wicked_pdf_stylesheet_link_tag "pdf" -%>
</head>
<body>
<div class="container">
<table>
<td><%= wicked_pdf_image_tag "sjit.png" %></td>
<td>
  <center>
    <h2 >International Conference in Recent Trends and Engineering Technology</h2>
    <h4>Organized by</h4>
    <h2>St.Joseph's Institue of Technology</h2><br><br>
    <h3>Conference Ticket</h3>
  </center>
</td>
<td><%= wicked_pdf_image_tag "icrtet.png" %></td>
</table>
<div class="col-md-12">
    <b>First Name</b>  :  <%= current_user.first_name%><br>
    <b>Last Name</b>   :  <%= current_user.last_name%><br>
    <b>Email id</b>    :  <%= current_user.email%><br>
    <b>DD Number</b>   :  <%= current_user.payment_detail.dd_number%><br>
    <b>Amount</b>      :  <%= current_user.payment_detail.amount %><br>
<br><b>Bring a copy of this while coming to the conference.</b><br>
<h3>General Information</h3>
<h4>
  Submission of Papers</h4>
<ul>
<li>      Authors are required to submit their papers (maximum of 8 A4 sized pages) adhering to the IEEE specified format (a copy of which is available for download in the site).</li>
<li>   Authors must upload their papers onto the conference website.</li>
<li>      The submitted papers must be original and unpublished.</li>
<li>      Double blind peer reviews will be followed.</li>
<li>      Registrations must be done online and a scanned copy of the Demand Draft must be enclosed with it.</li>
<li>      The DD must be drawn in favour of "St.Joseph's Institute of Technology", payable within Chennai at any nationalised bank.</li>
<li>      Selected papers will be pubished in Annexure I/Annexure II.</li>
</ul>
<h4>Event Registration</h4>
<ul>
<li>    The Demand Draft for the required amount must be drawn.</li>
<li>    The DD number must be entered along with the name of the bank and branch.</li>
<li>    The scanned copy of the DD must be uploaded.</li>

</ul>


</div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
